{"tid":1401773,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"百老匯會員部-有關8月5號之特殊服務安排","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T07:09:10.000Z","uid":109127,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e988941051adaa7155044f1f01bbde6a6db1c866","tid":1401773,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"親愛的會員：<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 鑑於8月5日可能面臨全港罷工罷市之情況，如本會未能或提供有限度服務情況下，將有如下特殊安排，謹奉詳情:<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n歸還借用物品: 閣下如有於8月5號到期歸還之物品，可提早於8月4號(星期日)或延遲至8月6號(星期一)內歸還，而不當作逾期歸還 及 免除額外罰款。<br />\n<br />\n如於8月7號或之後歸還，則作正常逾期計算(每項借用物品每天罰款為港幣＄１０)。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n入會及續會: 閣下可透過會員專頁或手機程式，在網上申請會藉或登入續會。<br />\n<br />\n會員專頁: <a href=\"https://bc.cinema.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbc.cinema.com.hk%2F&d=DXsCe6mrroMB06wP0eqGVcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=f7516a14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bc.cinema.com.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n  *** 網上入會或續會須於一個月內親臨油麻地百老匯電影中心-會員部領取相關贈券。***<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港加油!</span><br />\n<br />\n百老匯電影中心啟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以後睇戲都會去百老匯電影中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3aeef6c6d1455e86efc39424ce9b66117e25b3","tid":1401773,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7eab6ca1d6ad9cb7eb23a45bf44b4cf3f0c8ee02","tid":1401773,"uid":70013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e988941051adaa7155044f1f01bbde6a6db1c866","tid":1401773,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"親愛的會員：<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 鑑